    </a><a href="#whatisthepurposeofasuccessionplan" class="cursor-pointer font-400 text-charcoal/70 inline-block text-[14px] leading-[24px] tracking-[0.1px] md:text-[16px] md:tracking-[0.15px]">2. What is the Purpose of a Succession Plan?
    </a><a href="#whyissuccessionplanningimportant" class="cursor-pointer font-400 text-charcoal/70 inline-block text-[14px] leading-[24px] tracking-[0.1px] md:text-[16px] md:tracking-[0.15px]">3. Why is Succession Planning Important?
    </a><a href="#whoisresponsibleforsuccessionplanning" class="cursor-pointer font-400 text-charcoal/70 inline-block text-[14px] leading-[24px] tracking-[0.1px] md:text-[16px] md:tracking-[0.15px]">4. Who is Responsible for Succession Planning?
